                    <p className="text-xl md:text-2xl opacity-90 font-light max-w-lg leading-relaxed text-white text-left animate-slide-in-right delay-100">Deliverable. Achievable. <br/>We'll set the way.</p>
                    <div className="mt-8 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm opacity-60 text-white font-bold tracking-widest uppercase animate-fade-in-up delay-300">
